OL,3,CBusinesses claim to be out of pocket
OL,4,Cafter events company failed to pay on
OL,5,Ctime
OL,7,FSeveral venues across Wales say
OL,8,Fthey've been left out of pocket for
OL,9,Fmonths after an events company used
OL,10,Ftheir facilities and did not pay on
OL,11,Ftime.
OL,13,FClimax Promotions and Events Limited -
OL,14,Fwho also go by the name of Escape
OL,15,FRecords - have been accused of leaving
OL,16,Fsome businesses across Wales thousands
OL,17,Fof pounds short and causing
OL,18,Freputational damage.
