OL,7,FOne venue whose owners say they were
OL,8,Fnot paid on time is Gwyrch Castle in
OL,9,FAbergele. The location shot to fame in
OL,10,F2020 when it became host for ITV's I'm
OL,11,Fa Celebrity Get Me Out of Here and is
OL,12,Fowned by a trust who are trying to
OL,13,Fraise funds to restore it.
OL,15,FKevin Lott who is the General Manager
OL,16,Fat Gwyrch Castle said they were first
OL,17,Fapproached by Climax Events and
OL,18,FPromotions in 2024 to host a halloween
OL,19,Fevent at the castle.
