OL,5,Ctime
OL,7,FThe trust at the castle agreed for the
OL,8,Fevent to take place having worked with
OL,9,Fthe company the previous year. However
OL,10,Fthey say that as the event drew to a
OL,11,Fclose they were still owed #5,000 by
OL,12,Fthe organisers.
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV Cymru Wales Kevin
OL,15,Fsaid: "We basically told them that if
OL,16,Fthey didn't pay up, we wouldn't open
OL,17,Fthe gate for them on the final weekend
OL,18,Fof the event.
