OL,7,F"They paid half, so we got #2,500. And
OL,8,Fwe accepted, let the event take place.
OL,9,FAnd that next #2,500 became our fight
OL,10,Ffor the next six to eight months with
OL,11,Fthem". The fee was eventually settled
OL,12,Fout of court for a lesser amount.
OL,14,FKevin says an event held by Climax
OL,15,Falso resulted in complaints from
OL,16,Flocals due to the noise, causing the
OL,17,Fcastle reputational and financial loss.
