OL,7,FClimax Promotions and Events
OL,8,Facknowledged that the dispute over the
OL,9,Ffinal payment for the hire of Gwrych
OL,10,FCastle was settled out of court for a
OL,11,Freduced amount. They also strongly
OL,12,Frejected they were responsible for the
OL,13,Fnotice saying "at no point were we the
OL,14,Flicense holder at the venue; therefore
OL,15,Fthe venue would have been liable for
OL,16,Fany breaches of license conditions. At
OL,17,Fno point during the event did the
OL,18,Fvenue raise any noise issues with us."
