OL,7,F50 miles away in Holyhead, Antony
OL,8,FRowley who owns the Duke of Lancaster
OL,9,Fship says he has also been left
OL,10,Fwaiting for payments after the company
OL,11,Fhosted a 'scarefest' halloween event
OL,12,Fon board.
OL,14,FHe says that Climax Promotions and
OL,15,FEvents Limited have not paid for
OL,16,Fthousands of pounds worth of work that
OL,17,Fwas carried out on board or the final
OL,18,Fpayment for its hire.
