OL,7,FHe said: "It was the week before they
OL,8,Fwere holding the event and we said,
OL,9,F'You need to pay the two installments
OL,10,Fyou've missed, otherwise it's not
OL,11,Fgoing to go ahead'.
OL,13,F"So eventually, two days before, they
OL,14,Fpaid the next two instalments, which
OL,15,Fleft them one payment, which they said
OL,16,Fthey were going to pay 10 days after
OL,17,Fthe event finished, but they never
OL,18,Fpaid it".
