OL,7,FClimax Promotions and Events Limited,
OL,8,Fwho also go by the name Escape
OL,9,FRecords, claim the Duke of Lancaster
OL,10,Fvenue was "not fit for purpose" and
OL,11,Fsay they 'were forced to complete
OL,12,Fnumerous works that we were not made
OL,13,Faware of pre-event which cost
OL,14,Fthousands of pounds. These included a
OL,15,Fstructural survey, an asbestos survey
OL,16,Fand a fire risk assessment."
