OL,7,F"About February time they approached
OL,8,Fus. They were looking for a venue to
OL,9,Frun a Christmas event. We were more
OL,10,Fthan happy to look into it. They
OL,11,Foffered us tickets for the In It
OL,12,FTogether Festival. When we realized
OL,13,Fthey ran that, we thought, 'Okay, this
OL,14,Fmust be a really good company to work
OL,15,Fwith'".
OL,17,FWhile some staff members and two
OL,18,Fdirectors work for both the company
OL,19,Fbehind the Christmas event, and the In
OL,20,FIt Together Festival, they are two
OL,21,Fseparate legal companies.
