OL,7,FCatherine says it was shortly after
OL,8,Fsigning the initial agreement that
OL,9,Fthings started to go wrong.
OL,11,F"The first lot of payments just didn't
OL,12,Fcome in. So I negotiated with their
OL,13,Fmanager a revised payment schedule,
OL,14,Fand that was agreed, and they made two
OL,15,Fout of three payments. The third one
OL,16,Fbeing due on the 28th of December,
OL,17,Fjust before our pay date, hasn't come
OL,18,Fin".
